          "explanation": "Tall = alto (for people). \"He is a tall man.\""
        },
        {
          "id": "q2",
          "type": "multiple-choice",
          "question": "\"She is a ___, ___ woman.\" (amable, joven)",
          "options": [
            "kind, young",
            "young, kind",
            "big, old",
            "small, new"
          ],
          "correct": 0,
          "explanation": "Opinion (kind) before age (young): \"She is a kind, young woman.\""
        },
        {
          "id": "q3",
